## Summary
This documentation details the Batch destination integration for Amplitude, which allows syncing user cohorts to Batch's customer engagement platform for targeted push notifications and emails, with two destination options: Batch (Profile) for omnichannel projects and Batch for specific apps/websites, requiring matching identifiers between platforms.

